#ELLEFirstComeFirstSee: SAND by Shirin has arrived in Mumbai. The brand just opened its very first store at Jio World Drive, Mumbai and it feels exactly like stepping into it's world. Founded by Shirin Mann, the space is warm, earthy, sculptural, and filled with the kind of effortless energy SAND is known for. As the label nears five years, this new flagship marks a big moment for the brand. As the label approaches five years, this flagship is more than a store. It is an experience, a feeling, and a home for the SAND woman.
