@poster__girl__official has always done things their way and entirely on their own terms. Now, in partnership with OnlyFans, they're taking that ethos further than ever with an exclusive latex capsule collection.
We sat down with the founders to talk autonomy, breaking industry rules and why OnlyFans feels like the most natural home for a brand that has never needed anyone's permission.
Credit: POSTER GIRL

@tokibunbun & @fernandogarciam1205 are “popping the cherry” on their new era. This is @monsemaison 2.0, so to speak, and the first collection they’ve designed in its entirety since departing Oscar de la Renta. And as such, it has a distinct new flavor. 🍒
Inspired by real life cool girls like @chrisellelim and @mollyddickson to name a few, the brand which originally started in 2015 still has the same great taste with a fresh “addictive” recipe for the red carpet Get a second helping at the link in @instylemagazine’s bio now. 🥧
